latestPosts.caption:
For our sashing ceremony, I had the honour of wearing an exquisite suit by the legendary Rohit Bal — a name that has defined Indian couture for decades.

His menswear has always stood as a symbol of timeless elegance, intricate craftsmanship, and royal grandeur. Known for weaving India’s rich heritage into contemporary silhouettes, his designs have graced some of the most iconic moments in fashion history.

Wearing his creation for such a meaningful occasion made it all the more special. Super honoured to finally receive the sash of India. Heart full of gratitude 🇮🇳
